column1: Students should follow the School Library
Regulations regarding borrowing and dates for returning books.
Students who do not return their library books on time will be reported to their parents, and subjected to penalty fee of delay in returning the book(s) they borrowed.
If books are lost or damaged, he has to pay the price(s) of the book(s) in question.",,,,"The school library has a wide collection of books and other study material suitable for students.
Students should follow the School Library
Regulations regarding borrowing and dates for returning books.
Students who do not return their library books on time will be reported to their parents, and subjected to penalty fee of delay in returning the book(s) they borrowed.
